Class Utilization_warningValueOutputController

        • aspguidp.controller.output.element.impl.Utilization_warningValueOutputController

  • public class Utilization_warningValueOutputController
extends ValueOutputController
    Controller class for a value output component.

    A value output component contains an arbitrary number of output value labels. Each output value label is assigned to an output value. For each output value of the application exists a DataServicePool instance, which holds service instances and other data related information for the output value.

    An output value label displays the value which is managed by the ValueDataManager of the data service pool of the assigned output value.

    Additionally, a value output component can be assigned to a condition atom. If the condition atom is not empty, the output component is only displayed, if the current displayed answer set contains the condition atom of the output component (ConditionStatementService).

    • Method Detail

      • initialize

        protected void initialize()
        Initialization method which is called when the respective .fxml file is loaded.

        This method initializes a condition statement handler with the condition atom of the output component, to hide the output component when the condition atom is not present in the currently displayed answer set.

        Furthermore, this method initializes all output value labels of the value output component with the data service pool of the respective output value.
